</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
'ROUNDHOUSE' FOR ALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Just a quick thank you for the story on Nick-at-Nite's "Roundhouse" (TV Times, 
June 19).However, the very last line was wrong. It says "for ages 6 to 16." I'm 
almost 37 and I just don't miss "Roundhouse." The cast is uniformly talented 
and appealing, the music and lyrics to the songs are quite excellent for a 
weekly series, and the writing is outstanding. ... I wish I had "Roundhouse" 
when I was in school. 
</P>
<P>
 Charlie Andrews, West Hollywood 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
