<P>
 *** Shanice, "21 . . . Ways to Grow," Motown. Many young female singers would 
like to grow up to be Janet Jackson, but few have as good a shot at it as 
Shanice.On this coming-of-age album, the veteran recording artist celebrates 
adulthood with her most mature effort yet, a cohesive collection of playful 
