 Thank you, Messrs. Marking and Doodle (a.k.a. B. Dirk Yarborough and Jim 
Levisee). The editors, taking a cue from Chris Willman's Times review last week 
of the VH-1 Honors show, are partial to the name TAFKAP (The Artist Formerly 
Known as Prince).  
