<P>
 If Norway seemed too far to travel for the Olympic ice-skating competition, 
how does Idaho sound? Some of the biggest names in skating are performing at 
the Sun Valley Summer Ice Shows in Sun Valley through mid-September.The lineup 
includes Nancy Kerrigan, Brian Orser and Katarina Witt. General admission is 
