COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTH: SOUTH-CENTRAL; FREE IMMUNIZATIONS AT WOOTEN CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Al Wooten Jr. Heritage Center, at 9106 S. Western Ave., is sponsoring free 
immunizations for youngsters from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. July 18. 
</P>
<P>
 The shots include vaccines for measles, polio, mumps, diphtheria, tetanus and 
rubella. Tuberculosis screenings will also be offered. 
