<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP USA '94 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * EDITOR: Van Nightingale 
</P>
<P>
 * ASSISTANT EDITOR: Dave Morgan 
</P>
<P>
 * COPY EDITORS: Emilio Garcia-Ruiz, Steve Horn, Mike James, Rod Millie, Dave 
Moylan, Fred Robledo 
</P>
