<HEADLINE>
<P>
2 EJECT SAFELY IN TEXAS NATIONAL GUARD JET CRASH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Texas Air National Guard fighter jet crashed Friday in a remote area in the 
southwest part of the state, but the two crew members ejected and were reported 
to be safe, military authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 The crash involved a McDonnell Douglas F-16B. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
