<P>
 A top immigration official stands accused of making as much as $1 million by 
selling green cards for illegal immigrants. 
</P>
<P>
 Justice Department investigators said William Malcolm Tait had bypassed 
Immigration and Naturalization Service controls since 1983 to help a man obtain 
