<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070394-0393 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 057857 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 3, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Page 53; Calendar Desk 
